---
import BhargavLayout from "../../../layouts/BhargavLayout.astro";
---



<BhargavLayout title="Photobook | Bhargav">
  <main class="content-page">
    <header class="content-header">
      <div class="section-kicker">In progress</div>
      <h1 class="page-title">Photobook</h1>
      <p class="content-intro">
        A long-form body of work exploring sequence, memory and place through photography.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="photobook-hero">
      <img src="/images/photo-01.svg" alt="" />
    </div>

    <section class="content-block">
      <h2>Current direction</h2>
      <p>
        This project is developing as an extended visual sequence shaped by coastal memory,
        atmosphere and recurrence. More details and previews will be added here as the work evolves.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="content-block">
      <h2>Notes</h2>
      <p>
        The photobook gathers images into a slower narrative space, where light, distance and place
        can be held in relation rather than as isolated frames.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</BhargavLayout>